		    <title class="- topic/title ">
			      <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">5.406</ph> Public disclosure of justification documents for certain contract actions.</title>
		    <conbody class="- topic/body concept/conbody ">
			      <ol id="d343e13" class="- topic/ol ">
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d350e17" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            Justifications and approvals for other than full and open competition must be posted in accordance with <xref href="FAR-i1119843.dita#i1119843"
                        base="i1119843"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">6.305</xref>.</p>
				        </li>
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d350e29" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            Limited-source justifications (excluding brand name) for FSS orders or blanket purchase agreements with an estimated value greater than the simplified acquisition threshold must be posted in accordance with <xref href="FAR-i1117840.dita#i1117840"
                        base="i1117840"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">8.405-6</xref>(a)(2).</p>
				        </li>
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d350e41" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(c)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            Justifications for task or delivery orders greater than the simplified acquisition threshold and awarded without providing for fair opportunity must be posted in accordance with <xref href="FAR-i1104008.dita#i1104008"
                        base="i1104008"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">16.505</xref>(b)(2)(ii)(D).</p>
				        </li>
			      </ol>
